tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE coaches (
	coach_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	coach_name TEXT,
	certifications TEXT[],
	training_schedules JSONB,
	performance_evaluations JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE coach_information (
    coach_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    coach_name TEXT,
    certifications TEXT[],
    training_schedules JSON,
    performance_evaluations JSON
);

CREATE TABLE training_schedule (
    schedule_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    schedule_name TEXT,
    coach_id UUID REFERENCES coach_information(coach_id),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);
CREATE TABLE coaches (coach_id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), certification VARCHAR(50))
CREATE TABLE training_schedules (schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY, coach_id INT, schedule_date DATE, start_time TIME, end_time TIME, location VARCHAR(50))
CREATE TABLE performance_evaluations (evaluation_id INT PRIMARY KEY, coach_id INT, evaluation_date DATE, evaluation_score INT, feedback TEXT)

CREATE TABLE coach_info (
    coach_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    coach_name TEXT,
    certification TEXT,
    training_schedule TEXT,
    performance_evaluation TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE training_schedule (
    schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    schedule_date DATE,
    start_time TIME,
    end_time TIME,
    coach_id INT REFERENCES coach_info(coach_id)
);

CREATE TABLE coaching_sessions (
	session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	coach_id INT,
	client_id INT,
	session_date DATE,
	session_duration INT
);
